This paper is about improving neural architecture search for image classifiers, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a novel technique based on knowledge distillation, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper uses experiments to evaluate the performance of the proposed algorithm, which involves data analysis and statistical modeling (cs.DS).
